.TH "hwmp_route_info_get" 9 "hwmp_route_info_get" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
hwmp_route_info_get \- Update routing info to originator and transmitter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "u32" hwmp_route_info_get
.BI "(struct ieee80211_sub_if_data *sdata "  ","
.BI "struct ieee80211_mgmt *mgmt "  ","
.BI "const u8 *hwmp_ie "  ","
.BI "enum mpath_frame_type action "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "sdata" 12
local mesh subif
.IP "mgmt" 12
mesh management frame
.IP "hwmp_ie" 12
hwmp information element (PREP or PREQ)
.IP "action" 12
type of hwmp ie
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function updates the path routing information to the originator and the
transmitter of a HWMP PREQ or PREP frame.
.SH "RETURN"
metric to frame originator or 0 if the frame should not be further
processed
.SH "NOTES"
this function is the only place (besides user-provided info) where
path routing information is updated.
